demand-hopes-chinas-looser-monetary-policy-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称，中国海军的部署与其他大型演习一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-naval-deployments-line-with-other-large-drills-us-official-says-2024-12-11/</link><description>一位不愿透露姓名的美国军方官员周二表示，中国在东海和南海的海军部署有所增加，但与过去的其他大型演习一致。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-naval-deployments-line-with-other-large-drills-us-official-says-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>亚行下调亚洲发展中国家经济增长预期，并提示美国政策风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/adb-trims-developing-asias-growth-forecast-flags-us-policy-risks-2024-12-11/</link><description>亚洲开发银行周三表示，今年和明年亚洲发展中国家的增长速度可能比此前预期的要慢，如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普迅速改变美国贸易政策，前景可能会恶化。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/adb-trims-developing-asias-growth-forecast-flags-us-policy-risks-2024-12-11/</guid></item><item><title>据日经新闻报道，日产在管理层改组中将首席财务官马云重新任命为中国区负责人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/nissan-cfo-ma-head-china-management-reshuffle-nikkei-says-2024-12-10/</link><description>据《日经新闻》报道，日产汽车董事会已决定重新任命首席财务官马云来领导其中国业务，这对这家遭受危机打击的日本汽车制造商来说是一次高调的重组，因为该公司裁员数千人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 23:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/boards-policy-regulation/nissan-cfo-ma-head-china-management-reshuffle-nikkei-says-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：把筹码从桌面上拿下来，寻求中国的澄清</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-10/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:55:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯机构报道俄罗斯安全官员梅德韦杰夫抵达中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-security-official-medvedev-arrives-china-russian-agencies-report-2024-12-10/</link><description>据俄罗斯新闻机构周二晚间报道，俄罗斯高级安全官员德米特里·梅德韦杰夫抵达北京，与中国领导人进行为期两天的会谈。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:20:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-security-official-medvedev-arrives-china-russian-agencies-report-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥下议院一致批准针对应用程序工人的劳工改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-lower-house-approves-labor-reform-app-workers-2024-12-10/</link><description>墨西哥下议院周二批准了一项改革，旨在通过确保获得社会保障和圣诞奖金等福利来规范滴滴、Rappi 和 Uber 等应用程序的送货员和司机的劳动条件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-lower-house-approves-labor-reform-app-workers-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>瑞穗董事小林表示企业不应对特朗普的关税威胁反应过度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/mizuho-director-kobayashi-says-companies-should-not-overreact-trumps-tariff-2024-12-10/</link><description>日本瑞穗金融、欧姆龙和全日空的董事小林泉周二表示，企业不应对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国商品征收关税的威胁反应过度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/mizuho-director-kobayashi-says-companies-should-not-overreact-trumps-tariff-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国因可能致命的勒索软件攻击而制裁中国公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-sanctions-chinese-firm-over-potentially-deadly-ransomware-attack-2024-12-10/</link><description>美国因一家中国网络安全公司实施了一次雄心勃勃的网络攻击而对其实施制裁，美国财政部官员称该攻击可能导致人员死亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 16:43:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-sanctions-chinese-firm-over-potentially-deadly-ransomware-attack-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国因人权问题对两家中国企业实施贸易限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-trade-restrictions-two-chinese-firms-over-human-rights-2024-12-10/</link><description>周二，美国将两家中国公司列入贸易限制名单，理由是它们涉嫌助长侵犯人权行为，而总统乔·拜登在其执政的最后几天继续向北京施压。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:04:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-trade-restrictions-two-chinese-firms-over-human-rights-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国复星旅文将通过回购股份实现私有化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-fosun-take-tourism-unit-private-125-bln-deal-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国复星旅文拟回购非控股股东持有的股份，以实现私有化并解决对其股票流动性有限的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 10:58:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-fosun-take-tourism-unit-private-125-bln-deal-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis与中国宁德时代将投资43.3亿美元在西班牙建设电动汽车电池工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-chinas-catl-invest-433-bln-ev-battery-factory-spain-2024-12-10/</link><description>受较低成本和政府资助的鼓励，Stellantis 和中国电池制造商 CATL 将投资 41 亿欧元（43.3 亿美元）在西班牙建设欧洲最大的电动汽车电池工厂之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:25:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-chinas-catl-invest-433-bln-ev-battery-factory-spain-2024-12-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>